\max_{i\in I(\boldsymbol{\alpha}^{k})}-\nabla f(\boldsymbol{\alpha})_{i}+\min_{j\in I(\boldsymbol{\alpha}^{k})}\nabla f(\boldsymbol{\alpha})_{j}\le\epsilon\end{equation}

